methods.name: getActiveIndex
methods.docs: Get the index of the active slide.

methods.docs: Get the index of the previous slide.

methods.docs: Get whether or not the current slide is the first slide.

methods.name: isEnd
methods.docs: Get whether or not the current slide is the last slide.

methods.name: length
methods.docs: Get the total number of slides.

methods.name: lockSwipeToNext
methods.docs: Lock or unlock the ability to slide to the next slides.

methods.name: lockSwipeToPrev
methods.docs: Lock or unlock the ability to slide to the previous slides.

methods.name: lockSwipes
methods.docs: Lock or unlock the ability to slide to change slides.

methods.name: slideTo
methods.signature: slideTo(index: number, speed?: number, runCallbacks?: boolean) => Promise<void>

methods.name: update
methods.docs:
Update the underlying slider implementation. Call this if you've added or removed
child slides.
